{
  "text": "Property b) is related to input-output (BIBO) stability and disturbance rejection. It shows that the hypercube {x \u2208 R n : x \u2264 \u03b3} is dinvariant [CITATION_1] , that is, all trajectories initiating inside this cube remain there for all admissible perturbations.",
